place.name: CANOL
place.gazetteerText: PARCEL-CANOL, a township in Llanbadarn-Fawr parish, Cardigan; near Aberystwith and the river Rheidol. Acres, 4, 325. Real property, £4, 188; of which £2, 448are in mines. Pop., 604. Houses, 116. (In 1870-72, John Marius Wilson's Imperial Gazetteer of England and Wales)
